## Open-Source Libraries and Tools Referenced

The project ecosystem has studied or referenced the following open-source libraries for PLC protocol and file-format research. Their original licenses apply to their own code:

- [awlsim](https://github.com/mhatter/awlsim) — Siemens AWL/SCL simulator and toolchain.
- [DotNetSiemensPLCToolBoxLibrary](https://github.com/dotnetprojects/DotNetSiemensPLCToolBoxLibrary) — .NET library for Siemens S7 communication and project handling.
- [HslCommunication](https://github.com/dathlin/HslCommunication) — .NET industrial communication library.
- [rz-libmc7](https://github.com/romanetz/rz-libmc7) — Siemens S7 MC7 binary research utilities.
- [awltool](https://github.com/romanetz/awltool) — AWL tooling.
- [Stp7Toolbox](https://github.com/romanetz/Stp7Toolbox) — STEP 7 research toolbox.
- [ladder_drive](https://github.com/ladder-drive) / [ladder_converter](https://github.com/ladder-converter) — ladder-logic conversion research.
- [fx5_mbtcpserver](https://github.com/fx5-mbtcpserver) — Mitsubishi FX5 Modbus TCP sample server.
- [go-mcprotocol](https://github.com/go-mcprotocol) — Go implementation of MELSEC communication protocol.
- [Mitsubishi-protocol-wireshark-plugin](https://github.com/Mitsubishi-protocol-wireshark-plugin) — Wireshark dissector for Mitsubishi protocols.

